  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You wake up in a strange, unfamiliar place.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Aim for the horizon...\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious voice echoes in your head.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First things first: take a leap of faith.</strong><br>Yes—<strong>jump off the base.</strong><br>That’s where the real journey begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t worry. No broken ankles. Promise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/ea6d05b1237edf50c75ed9e41cf92756.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/ea6d05b1237edf50c75ed9e41cf92756.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/ea6d05b1237edf50c75ed9e41cf92756.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Just go. As far as you can.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies start to appear once you’ve left the base behind.<br>Each time you die and return, the map and weather shift.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Depending on the weather, different enemies show up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeating enemies will sometimes reward you with materials—<br>and what you get depends on the type of enemy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💡 Hint:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sunny daytime is your best bet.<br>Find a <strong>Stone Golem</strong>, defeat it, and use the material it drops to craft your first tool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/16eb1e5a14be28f75588e79fb82225eb.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/16eb1e5a14be28f75588e79fb82225eb.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/16eb1e5a14be28f75588e79fb82225eb.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/417b0458bf38f71dbb620d436dfb0cca.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/417b0458bf38f71dbb620d436dfb0cca.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/417b0458bf38f71dbb620d436dfb0cca.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That’s how the building begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The enemies?<br>Well… they’re a little shy.<br>They might run away before you land a hit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think of it like fishing.<br>Every encounter is rare.<br>Sometimes, you’ll come back empty-handed.<br>That’s okay.<br><strong>Try again tomorrow—maybe it’ll be a big haul.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn which enemies appear in which weather, and what they drop.<br>Don’t just rush in blindly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check your map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/08222b0d061a29dfe55ecaffe483a77c.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/08222b0d061a29dfe55ecaffe483a77c.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/08222b0d061a29dfe55ecaffe483a77c.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the terrain that gives <strong>you</strong> the upper hand—and strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up an <strong>alchemy desk</strong> and start your <strong>fields</strong>.<br>Grow vegetables. Improve breeds. Evolve your harvest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/d007454013371c2caca0edd5fcf6fbe2.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/d007454013371c2caca0edd5fcf6fbe2.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/d007454013371c2caca0edd5fcf6fbe2.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/3afccb561a624be21a9f0ab2d31821f0.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/3afccb561a624be21a9f0ab2d31821f0.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/3afccb561a624be21a9f0ab2d31821f0.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat what you grow. Feel yourself getting stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s no telling what kind of upgrades your crops will bring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/cd07e1cc941c1cc5da23f5cc0b3391e3.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/cd07e1cc941c1cc5da23f5cc0b3391e3.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/cd07e1cc941c1cc5da23f5cc0b3391e3.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a large number of disposal sites and automated drones and aim for the dream of a passive income life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/dbaa38c8c737037657448d31b32c32c6.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/dbaa38c8c737037657448d31b32c32c6.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/dbaa38c8c737037657448d31b32c32c6.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wise person once said:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"If you want to go far, just build a pole creator.\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/3355ad01a635f115df7ce54c0f847460.poster.avif?t=1750561919\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/3355ad01a635f115df7ce54c0f847460.webm?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495500/extras/3355ad01a635f115df7ce54c0f847460.mp4?t=1750561919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
